snippet.title: Bugsnax Launch Trailer - November 12th 2020 | PS5, PS4, Epic Games Store
snippet.description:
From the minds behind Octodad: Dadliest Catch comes Bugsnax, a whimsical adventure game coming to PlayStation 5, PlayStation 4, and Epic Games Store on November 12th 2020. 
https://www.bugsnax.com
